        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-20 18:45:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nWhich CI are we targeting here? ONAP CI is based on VMs, which means that nested VMs must already be supported on the host itself before we can bring up any VM in the CI job.\nFor CI specifically, we need something that can be brought up in a VM via containers only. Eg: KIND or something like that.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "017dc2040dee7684dfb8f811eee6d88f6c71796b",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3957,
